makedeb tool; equivalent of makepkg from Slackware

usage:
***
makedeb ep <filename.deb> [nodeps] - Entire Package building
***
makedeb md <filename.deb> - pack control.tar.gz data.tar.lzma to .deb file
makedeb mm - make md5sums file
makedeb mc - make control.tar.gz file
makedeb hp <filename.deb> - Half Package building
makedeb bp - adjust binary deps in control file
